<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Diagnóstico - Admin</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-950 min-h-screen text-white">
<div class="flex min-h-screen">

  <%- include('../partials/admin-sidebar') %>

  <main class="ml-60 flex-1 p-8">

    <div class="mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">§ Diagnóstico de Pagamentos</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-1 text-sm">Verifique se as credenciais e conexµes estão configuradas corretamente.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-3">

      <% resultados.forEach(function(r) { %>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border <%= r.ok ? 'border-green-800' : 'border-red-800' %> rounded-xl px-5 py-4 flex items-start gap-4">
        <span class="text-2xl mt-0.5"><%= r.ok ? '<span style="display:flex;align-items:center;width:20px;height:20px;"><%- icon('check', 'w-5 h-5') %></span>' : '<span style="display:flex;align-items:center;width:20px;height:20px;"><%- icon('error', 'w-5 h-5') %></span>' %></span>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="font-semibold text-white text-sm"><%= r.nome %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-400 mt-1 truncate"><%= r.valor %></div>
          <% if (r.dica) { %>
            <div class="text-xs text-red-400 mt-1.5 bg-red-950/50 rounded px-2 py-1"><%= r.dica %></div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }) %>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 max-w-2xl bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-white mb-3"> Como obter as credenciais</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-400">

        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Mercado Pago (credenciais de teste)</p>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Acesse <span class="font-mono text-blue-400">mercadopago.com.br</span>  Entre na conta</li>
            <li>Vá em <strong class="text-gray-200">Seu negócio  Configuraçµes  Credenciais</strong></li>
            <li>Selecione aba <strong class="text-gray-200">Credenciais de teste</strong></li>
            <li>Copie o <strong class="text-gray-200">Access Token</strong> (começa com <span class="font-mono">TEST-</span>) e a <strong class="text-gray-200">Public Key</strong></li>
            <li>Cole no <span class="font-mono">.env</span>:
              <pre class="bg-gray-800 rounded px-3 py-2 mt-1 text-xs text-green-300 overflow-x-auto">MP_ACCESS_TOKEN=TEST-xxxxxxxxxxxx
MP_PUBLIC_KEY=TEST-xxxxxxxxxxxx</pre>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">SumUp</p>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Acesse <span class="font-mono text-blue-400">developer.sumup.com</span>  Login</li>
            <li>Crie um app ou use o padrão  copie a <strong class="text-gray-200">API Key</strong></li>
            <li>O <strong class="text-gray-200">Merchant Code</strong> está em <em>Profile  Account</em></li>
            <li>Cole no <span class="font-mono">.env</span>:
              <pre class="bg-gray-800 rounded px-3 py-2 mt-1 text-xs text-green-300 overflow-x-auto">SUMUP_API_KEY=sup_sk_xxxxxxxxxxxx
SUMUP_MERCHANT_CODE=MXXXXXXXX</pre>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Após editar o .env</p>
          <p>Reinicie o servidor: <span class="font-mono text-yellow-300">node server.js</span> (ou Ctrl+C e inicie novamente)</p>
          <p class="mt-1">Então recarregue esta página para ver o status atualizado.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
      <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline text-sm">» Atualizar diagnóstico</a>
      &nbsp;Â&nbsp;
      <a href="/admin/configuracoes" class="text-gray-400 hover:underline text-sm"> Configuraçµes</a>
    </div>

  </main>
</div>
</body>
</html>
